Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本作品是設想在首都東京地區發生巨大地震災害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在充分調查與查證的基礎上所製作的虛構故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原作力求體現真實性 通過模擬實驗而著成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也存在與現實事物描寫方式不同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:01:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的煙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在做夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:12.30,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「 燃 燒 、大 橋 」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個姐姐去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 不要什麼都問姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你說沒事的 一旦發生什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們兩個也能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 手機能打通嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 媽媽沒受傷就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們沒事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 爸爸和媽媽沒事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯繫不上 你問我 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是和你說過了 不要什麼都問我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位 肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子一餓 人就會變得焦燥不安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 早飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我真理就行了 悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是飯糰子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不介意的話 未來也吃點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飲料也有的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起在非常時刻 有時便利店會分發食物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去看了看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上醒來 發現你不在 還以為你先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來 我不在覺得很孤單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們做個約定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始我不會單獨行動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要離開肯定會向你們匯報行蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼對待我們如此親切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你孩子還在家裡等你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有我們這個包袱的話 你就能更快的回到家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你說得沒錯 我們的家在同一個方向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這也是一種緣分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們能在一起的時候在一起吧 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒關係嗎 我們會拖累你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:05:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了飯糰子 肚子一餓就會變得膽小
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們打起精神 一起加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有金槍魚 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的飯糰子是鮭魚餡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 真得是好熱 已經全身是汗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是個盛夏日 看這樣子接近40度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理說話真像我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然經常有人這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來 你說得太直白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:05:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我渴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天悠貴買了飲料 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收看下新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得太多的話手機會沒電
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看一下就馬上關掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}信息讀取中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}選台中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡 我們再次報導首都圈內地震受災情況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的交通工具都暫停運行 現在還沒有恢復的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始實施第一次交通管制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接多摩川 國道246號線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及環形7號線的內側區域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經全面禁止車輛通行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,截至目前為止 已經確認死亡者843名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:07:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有大量的行蹤不明者和輕重傷者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計今後這個數字還將持續增加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有這麼多人遇難
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止 一部分火災還沒有撲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在火災發生區附近的居民請盡快到避難所避難
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 大量的受災者步行回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有請京阪大學災害研究所研究員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村田規明教授 為我們講一下今後的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於這次地震直接造成回家困難者預計將達到650萬人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於餘震 今後將會持續多久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概未來三天還會發生5級以上的地震
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然大家都在走著回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況 誰也不知道什麼時候電車能正常運行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我們也走回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了飯糰子 我已經打起了精神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們家在瀨田川 很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是輕輕鬆鬆就能走到的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說台場孤立無援 是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡橋被燒燬 到處都已禁止通行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真糟糕 這邊不會沉沒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 這麼寬廣的地方不會說沉就沉沒的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是台場是人造陸地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來 這邊曬不到太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人擔心 連食物和水都沒帶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊 這邊也有居民 救援馬上會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對 家人在一起也算不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見到爸爸媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:09:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這麼想早一刻回到爸媽身邊 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是海上保安廳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們開始用水上巴士運送回家困難者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從台場出發至廣田碼頭方向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意回家者請到前方公園旁邊的碼頭集合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想坐船前往千葉方向的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像搭乘船能到達廣田碼頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不該穿涼鞋來 腳都磨破了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我家有孩子 創可貼是必需品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 是青蛙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐是青蛙星人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙星人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用多囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 我用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 萬一走不動了 我背你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說背你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 我又不是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺難受的時候說出來 我真的會背你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對我的腰腿充滿自信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人能走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這股氣勢 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳痛不痛 不用急 不要逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說這個 你說我們能乘上船嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想乘船的人這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐不上去的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們先去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理 你可真是沒神經
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說我積極樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 三 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝你 幫了我大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能和媽媽分開哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是太謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.99,0:12:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就要到碼頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理可真熱心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以說是多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明剛剛約定好要離開的時候 肯定會說明去向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 真理姐姐做了好事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去Big Sight的市民請向前直行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去濱松方向的市民請在前面的十字路口向左轉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了 這麼多人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回去的人全都來了這個方向
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走散了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來 我們也牽手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的 已經不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請你緊跟著我以防走失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你站在這裡礙事 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴 真理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要傻愣在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是牽著手走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要分開哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟爆炸一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高架都塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下糟了 橋已經完全不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能坐船了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本船將前去營救落水者 請大家換乘水上巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別乘坐這艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能放手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:16:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:16:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船馬上就要出發 體質虛弱的人請先乘坐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人 我們還是坐下一艘船為好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我們去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請要乘船者 請等下一艘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的孩子們 快點乘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等待下一艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請冷靜 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實不是最佳狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也總算坐上了船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薑還是老的辣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人說你孩子的媽 你還回答說是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實自從我老公去世以後 我變得越來越堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想即使一個人也要把陽菜養大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 橋一直在燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為好像油罐車著火了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.09,0:19:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 人都掉進海裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果晚一步 坐上那艘船就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 浪向這邊襲來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果坐上那艘船的話就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 讓你們遇到危險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.07,0:20:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 真理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.56,0:22:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京鐵塔坍塌 正在全力進行營救工作
